Package us.teaminceptus.novaconomy.api

Interface SortingType<T>

Type Parameters:
T - Type of parameter to compare
All Superinterfaces:
Comparator<T>
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface SortingType<T> extends Comparator<T>
Represents a Sorting Type for organizing a list of specific items.
